OL,5, Thousands of NHS staff across the UK   
OL,6, are facing pay cuts because of a change
OL,7, in Covid sickness policy.              
OL,9,FAnalysis by BBC Panorama suggests that 
OL,10,Fbetween 5,000 and 10,000 NHS workers   
OL,11,Fcould be off sick with long Covid.     
OL,13,FUnions are accusing the government of  
OL,14,Ffailing to support health staff who    
OL,15,Fworked during the coronavirus pandemic.
OL,17,FThe government says the Covid-19 public
OL,18,Finquiry will examine these issues when 
OL,19,Fit begins taking evidence in May.      
